<p><strong>Event keywords:</strong> "birthday cake order [city]," "catering coffee service [city]," "brunch spots [city]," "dessert table for party"</p>
<p><strong>Seasonal keywords:</strong> "pumpkin spice latte [city]," "Easter treats near me," "Valentine's Day cake order," "holiday cookie boxes near me"</p>
<p><strong>Discovery keywords:</strong> "best brunch [city]," "instagrammable cafes [city]," "quiet coffee shops to work [city]," "coffee shop with wifi near me"</p>
